{{ 'custom-cuehealth.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="ch-page-hero">
  <div class="ch-page-hero__inner">
    <p class="ch-page-hero__eyebrow">CueHealth Policies</p>
    <h1 class="ch-page-hero__heading">Shipping Policy</h1>
    <p class="ch-page-hero__sub">Fast, reliable delivery across India. Last updated: May 2026.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ch-policy-wrapper page-width">
  <div class="ch-policy-content">

    <div class="ch-policy-highlight">
      <span>🚚</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Free Shipping on orders above ₹499</strong>
        <p>Standard delivery across India in 3–7 working days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Order Processing Time</h2>
    <p>Orders are processed within <strong>1–2 working days</strong> (Monday to Saturday, excluding public holidays) after payment confirmation. You will receive an order confirmation email immediately after placing your order, and a dispatch notification with tracking details once your order is shipped.</p>

    <h2>2. Shipping Rates</h2>
    <table class="ch-policy-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Order Value</th>
          <th>Shipping Charge</th>
          <th>Estimated Delivery</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Below ₹499</td>
          <td>₹49</td>
          <td>3–7 working days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>₹499 and above</td>
          <td><strong>FREE</strong></td>
          <td>3–7 working days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Express (select pincodes)</td>
          <td>₹99</td>
          <td>1–2 working days</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Delivery Locations</h2>
    <p>We deliver <strong>pan-India</strong> — all states and union territories. Remote areas and certain island territories may require additional 2–3 days.</p>

    <h2>4. Cash on Delivery (COD)</h2>
    <p>COD is available on orders up to <strong>₹3,000</strong> in most serviceable pincodes. A nominal COD handling fee of ₹30 applies. COD availability is subject to your pincode — you will be notified at checkout if COD is unavailable for your location.</p>

    <h2>5. Order Tracking</h2>
    <p>Once your order is dispatched, you will receive:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>An email with your tracking number and carrier details</li>
      <li>An SMS/WhatsApp notification with a tracking link</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can also track your order by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in">hello@cuehealth.in</a> or WhatsApp at <a href="https://wa.me/917455918832">7455918832</a>.</p>

    <h2>6. Delays & Exceptions</h2>
    <p>CueHealth is not responsible for delays caused by:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Incorrect or incomplete shipping addresses provided by the customer</li>
      <li>Natural disasters, strikes, or other force majeure events</li>
      <li>Delays by third-party courier partners</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If your order is delayed by more than 10 working days, please contact us immediately and we will investigate.</p>

    <h2>7. Damaged / Lost Shipments</h2>
    <p>If your order arrives damaged or is lost in transit, please contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> with photos of the damaged package. We will arrange a free replacement or full refund at our discretion.</p>

    <div class="ch-policy-contact-bar">
      <p>Have a shipping question?</p>
      <div>
        <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in" class="ch-hero__btn ch-hero__btn--primary">Email Us</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/917455918832" target="_blank" class="ch-hero__btn ch-hero__btn--secondary">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping Policy Page",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "ch-policy-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Shipping Policy Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
